{
  "stem": "12506.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was shot on my shoulders, that was a pretty open wound at that time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was a miracle, that's what he said.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If he were doctor, he said to me, can you move your-- your legs?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Your back-- there was nothing paralyzed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He couldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, God was with you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, he certainly was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Did they ever tell you how they found you still alive, when so many had been killed?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First of all, the doctor told me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then after 50 years, we went to a hotel near New York, in Long Island, an orthodox hotel.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they had a pamphlet about the Jewish-- the Young Israel-- every season sends out a pamphlet like that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my wife was reading it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she says, hey, look, Cham is in this pamphlet.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I started to read.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was a group from Passaic that went to visit Flossenburg.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I found out things that over 50 years-- I-- I was reading books and films and everything else.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I never knew exactly what happened in that march when people left Flossenburg.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I know that I survived, but I didn't know exactly what happened.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I got a little more picture of that one.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because I was really unconscious.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But when I found out, I said, this is just unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "After 50 years, you come across something like this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I intended to get in touch with the rabbi from Passaic.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "When I go home, I will-- I will give it another shot.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "My wife had an operation, pretty heavy, and I couldn't get in touch with him before.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "According to this pamphlet, there were five people left alive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they have some names in it.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
